# lilbee demo
Output demo.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 3
Set Shell "bash"

Hide
Type "export COLUMNS=120"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "lilbee status"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "lilbee chat"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "What is the size of the engine in my Crown Vic?"
Enter
Sleep 30s

Type "What is the part number for my headlamps?"
Enter
Sleep 30s

Type "quit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
